  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/bcf2aa41390a91e5e14818b05a88c8c4.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=145 /></span><br><br><br>Freshly graduated, you and your team of mechanics must work together to repair as many cars as possible before your shift ends. Take part in an intense adventure, recruit the best mechanics and become true mechanic heroes together!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/989326d09282f0b7b6eaafc648579637.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=145 /></span><br><br><br>Playable with up to 4 players. In local and/or online multiplayer, work together to get the highest score and unlock new levels and characters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/d123aca710c0cd7aa0f7b5f79d852f58.poster.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/d123aca710c0cd7aa0f7b5f79d852f58.webm?t=1705160172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/496e51f4b5e669296c8ffd101745a0f1.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=145 /></span><br><br><br>Get ready to become an elite mechanic! Change the wheels, repair the body of the car or recharge the battery, car maintenance will no longer have any secrets for you!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/41ca6c49bc2f4f4b638a728e230150ba.poster.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/41ca6c49bc2f4f4b638a728e230150ba.webm?t=1705160172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>PHYSICS!</strong><br><br>Forget the safety rules and save time with hero physics. Throw tools, wheels or lightbulbs, it's much more convenient!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/06b8b4dc2c454ea5af62064e8f96d004.poster.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/06b8b4dc2c454ea5af62064e8f96d004.webm?t=1705160172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/e0aa0113a13808fb70a01d0963999d19.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=145 /></span><br><br><br>Travel the world, discover unique environments and complete complex tasks that will push your coordination skills to the limit. <br><br>Over 25 levels for you and your team to discover and master!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/35c68f07d75cfe6a94006764a5fec0d5.poster.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/35c68f07d75cfe6a94006764a5fec0d5.webm?t=1705160172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>COMPETITIVES RACES!</strong><br><br>Play against your friends in a competitive racing mode, because a team of mechanics always needs a driving champion!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/d38ca33c5a530c142df8c0e39bccc2da.poster.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/d38ca33c5a530c142df8c0e39bccc2da.webm?t=1705160172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/bcf2aa41390a91e5e14818b05a88c8c4.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=145 /></span><br><br><br>Freshly graduated, you and your team of mechanics must work together to repair as many cars as possible before your shift ends. Take part in an intense adventure, recruit the best mechanics and become true mechanic heroes together!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/989326d09282f0b7b6eaafc648579637.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=145 /></span><br><br><br>Playable with up to 4 players. In local and/or online multiplayer, work together to get the highest score and unlock new levels and characters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/d123aca710c0cd7aa0f7b5f79d852f58.poster.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/d123aca710c0cd7aa0f7b5f79d852f58.webm?t=1705160172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/496e51f4b5e669296c8ffd101745a0f1.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=145 /></span><br><br><br>Get ready to become an elite mechanic! Change the wheels, repair the body of the car or recharge the battery, car maintenance will no longer have any secrets for you!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/41ca6c49bc2f4f4b638a728e230150ba.poster.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/41ca6c49bc2f4f4b638a728e230150ba.webm?t=1705160172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>PHYSICS!</strong><br><br>Forget the safety rules and save time with hero physics. Throw tools, wheels or lightbulbs, it's much more convenient!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/06b8b4dc2c454ea5af62064e8f96d004.poster.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/06b8b4dc2c454ea5af62064e8f96d004.webm?t=1705160172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/e0aa0113a13808fb70a01d0963999d19.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=145 /></span><br><br><br>Travel the world, discover unique environments and complete complex tasks that will push your coordination skills to the limit. <br><br>Over 25 levels for you and your team to discover and master!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/35c68f07d75cfe6a94006764a5fec0d5.poster.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/35c68f07d75cfe6a94006764a5fec0d5.webm?t=1705160172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>COMPETITIVES RACES!</strong><br><br>Play against your friends in a competitive racing mode, because a team of mechanics always needs a driving champion!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/d38ca33c5a530c142df8c0e39bccc2da.poster.avif?t=1705160172\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2061620/extras/d38ca33c5a530c142df8c0e39bccc2da.webm?t=1705160172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
